\/18\/punishment-urine\/","url_meta":{"origin":34834,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Cleanliness: Punishment in grave due to soiling yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe majority of torment in the grave is due to carelessness with urine, so avoid soiling yourself with urine.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304raqut\u0323ni\u0304 466 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38826,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/18\/stomach-injuries-grave\/","url_meta":{"origin":34834,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Qabr: Those killed by stomach injuries not punished in grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Sulayman ibn Surad reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever is killed by a stomach injury will not be punished in his grave.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1064 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064f\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0635\u064f\u0631\u064e\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u06